items.name: Wildcard set mainly for random generation of Kawaii girls (主に美少女ランダム生成のためのワイルドカードセット)
items.description:
A beginner's article on dynamic prompts is available here.

If you have not used it yet, you may want to have a look through it.

DynamicPrompts Petit Course (StableDiffusion AUTOMATIC1111)

https://note.com/489_/n/nd9db7c79006a

,

Wildcard Set for Random Appearance Selection

,

Note: If you like it, please give it a STAR MARKS !

,

This wild card set may solve one of your problems.

Do you want AI to smelt a pretty girl today?

To do so, what is her hair style? Hair color? Eye color? Clothes? There are so many things to think about.

But today, you can put that hassle to rest!

,

Install the Dynamic Prompt extension, and then write the description as shown in the sample prompt.

All you have to do is press the generate button and wait.

It may not be your cup of tea, but it will generate cute little girls one after another without you having to think about it.

,

Sometimes you may find that you are making a big mistake.

But some of them may be your favorites mixed in.

You know that "Generate forever" that appears when you right-click on the generate button?

The machine will keep summoning girls forever until you voluntarily stop it.

,

But beware.

The girl on the screen is not necessarily SFW.

AI is very fickle.

I cannot be held responsible if something unforeseen happens in the office or while streaming.

Please be careful not to shorten your lifespan with long hours of smelting activities away from your seat.

And of course, it's no less taxing on your PC, right?

,

What if the wildcard file does not contain your favorite word?

The solution is simple.

Just open Notepad and edit the file as you like.

As you use it more and more, it will reflect your tastes and satisfy your proclivities.

,

Once you have your upgraded wildcard, it's your turn.

You can put it all together and upload it for someone else to use.

I'll keep working on upgrading mine.

,

How to use

The downloaded wildcard is in zip format, so please unzip it and save the contents to the given path.

Refer to the following for where to place the files.

InstallPath \stable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-dynamic-prompts\wildcards

,

note:Files with M at the end are for boys.

Clothing is not considered for adults

Because I don't have a taste for coordinating adults.

However, it is definitely possible to specify hair styles and colors.

,

If it doesn't work, the only way to deal with it is to do a few.

And don't get hung up on sample prompts.

Use your experience, especially with quality and negative tags.

If it still doesn't work...I suggest you erase everything and forget about it ;P

Thank you for your patience, it is much appreciated.

,

note:The reason I'm breaking the prompt multiple times is to make it easier to read later.

It doesn't have to be that identical.

The comma at the beginning of the line is included because the underscore will disappear if it is not included.

,

,

ダイナミックプロンプトについての初心者向け記事をこちらに用意しています。

まだ使ったことない方は目を通してもらうといいかもしれません。

DynamicPrompts プチ講座(StableDiffusion AUTOMATIC1111)

https://note.com/489_/n/nd9db7c79006a

,

ランダムに容姿を選択するためのワイルドカードセット

※ 気に入っていただけたならぜひ★をつけてください！

,

このワイルドカードセットは、あなたの悩みを一つ解決するかもしれません。

今日もAIにかわいい女の子を錬成してもらいたい？

そのために、髪型は？髪色は？目の色？洋服？、と考えることは山済みです。

しかし今日でその煩わしさとはおさらばしましょう！

,

ダイナミックプロンプトのエクステンションをインストールしてからサンプルプロンプトのように記述します。

あとは生成ボタンを押下して待つだけです。

あなたの好みではないかもしれませんが、何も考えなくても次々にかわいらしい少女が生み出されていきます。

,

時には大失敗していることもあるでしょう。

だが中にはあなたのお気に入りが混ざっているかもしれません。

生成ボタンを右クリックすると出てくる「Generate forever」はご存知ですか？

あなたが任意で停止させるまで、マシンは永遠に女の子を召喚し続けるでしょう。

,

しかし注意してください。

画面に登場している女の子が必ずしもSFWであるとは限りません。

AIはとても気まぐれなのですから。

もしオフィスやストリーミング中に不測の事態が起こった場合でも私は責任を取ることが出来ません。

席を離れての長時間にわたる錬成活動であなたの寿命を縮めないようご注意ください。

もちろんPCの負担も少なくありませんからね？

,

もしワイルドカードファイルの中身にあなたの好きなワードが入っていなかったら？

その解決は簡単です。

メモ帳を開いて好きなように編集すれば良いのです。

使いこむうちにあなたの好みが反映されて、より性癖を満たす物になるでしょう。

,

グレードアップしたワイルドカードが出来たなら次はあなたの出番です。

全てをまとめてからアップロードして誰かに使ってもらうことが出来るでしょう。

私も負けずにアップグレードに勤しみたいと思います。

,

使い方

ダウンロードしたファイルはzip形式になっていますので、解凍してから中身を所定のパスへ保存してください。

ファイルの置き場所は下記を参考のこと。

インストールパス \stable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-dynamic-prompts\wildcards

,

※末尾にMがついていファイルは男の子用です

　衣服については大人用を考慮していません

　なぜなら私には大人をコーディネートする趣味がないからです

　しかし髪型や色の指定は利用可能であることは間違いありません

,

うまくいかない場合の対処方法はひたすら数をこなすこと。

そしてサンプルプロンプトにこだわらないことです。

特にクオリティ系やネガティブのタグについては、今まで培ったあなたの経験を活かしてください。

それでもうまくいかない場合は・・・すべて消去して忘れてしまうことをお勧めします ;P

あなたの忍耐に感謝いたします。

,

※プロンプトを何度も改行しているのは後から見やすくするためです

　別にそこまで同じにする必要はありません

,

,

Steps: 20, Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras, CFG scale: 4, Seed: 1, Size: 384x512, Model hash: 55b3fdcfc6, Model: caulkinumV2_AR, Denoising strength: 0.6, ENSD: 31337, Hires upscale: 2, Hires steps: 20, Hires upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B

,

,

,

You can use it to highquality illustrations.

items.name: Zesshi Zetsumei【Antilene Heran Fouche】 绝死绝命【安缇莱涅·赫兰·芙什】(Overlord) Character Lora
items.description:
为什么我感觉我训练的人物lora都是一些比较冷门的角色……

算了这不重要。

这个Lora模型是基于final-prune.ckpt（【旧短哈希1d4a34af】新短哈希22fa233c2d），使用了768x768的数据集进行训练。

推荐权重为0.6-0.8.

如果人物无法生成你想要的动作，请增加动作的权重或者降低Lora的权重。

如果生成的人物图像面部不佳，推荐您勾选高清修复。

这个模型可以生成nsfw的图片。

相比于1.0版本，1.5版本能够提供更多的细节，但也更难操控。

测试了kotosmix以及AbyssOrangeMix2，AbyssOrangeMix3，以及anyhentai和Grapefruit，在使用高清修复时基本上都工作良好，1.5版本在不使用高清修复时可能会导致人物面部不佳。

英语是用Google翻译的，如果有造成误解之处非常抱歉。

Why do I feel that the lora characters I trained are all relatively unpopular characters...

Forget it is not important.

This Lora model is based on final-prune.ckpt ([old short hash 1d4a34af] new short hash 22fa233c2d), using a 768x768 dataset for training.

The recommended weight is 0.6-0.8.

If the character cannot generate the motion you want, please increase the weight of the motion or reduce the weight of Lora.

If the face of the generated character image is not good, it is recommended that you check HD Repair.

This model can generate pictures of nsfw.

Compared with version 1.0, version 1.5 can provide more details, but it is also more difficult to control.

I tested kotosmix, AbyssOrangeMix2, AbyssOrangeMix3, and anyhentai and Grapefruit, and they basically work well when using high-definition restoration. Version 1.5 may cause bad faces when not using high-definition restoration.

English is translated by Google, sorry if there is any misunderstanding.

items.name: Feet soles
items.description:
This model is mainly for inpainting or make soles closeups. as after my long struggling on soles lora, to train a good lora to generate feet soles pose is nearly impossible, this may need a complete checkpoint trainning. I don't like a lora model that can just use in few checkpoints or make image burning, so I think a model which just generate closeups may help people to inpaint soles in there workflow.

Feet soles is always rubbish in stable diffusion, for some models soles could be generated like something look like soles but still bad (there are still few models can generate soles not bad). This lora can lead model generate soles closeups with preserve the model's original style.

To use this lora model, you don't need any special tags, just prompt "soles", may "feet" in some models.

I recommand to use kohya additional networks extension to load the lora model.

 

此模型主要用于inpaint或者生成脚底的特写。在我长时间训练脚底lora的实验后，我发现要训练一个足够好的带有人像的脚底lora几乎是不可能的，这也许需要一个完整的大模型训练。我不喜欢一个只能在个别模型中良好使用的lora，或者让整个图片质量爆炸的lora，所以我做了这个仅供特写使用的V4版本。

在stable diffusion里， 脚底生成始终是一个大难题（多数模型都完全无法生成脚底，只有少数模型可以生成看起来像是脚底的东西，只有个别模型可以生成稍微好点的脚底）。这个lora模型可以在保留模型原有风格的情况下生成脚底特写.

只需要添加soles就可以，可能在部分模型中需要使用feet.

我推荐使用kohya additional networks扩展来加载此模型。

modelVersions.name: v3.1
modelVersions.description:
Trained with more full body shot, so this version can prevent the images from become just closeups of feet soles.

You need to use models that can generate legs ok, then use this lora, or you will get pretty bad results because the model you use would give you bad legs, then bad feet. The samples here is using hassanblend1512, dreamshaper, conterfeit2.5, lulubearmix.

items.description:
🧡 Please Review 🧡

❤️ Support Sexy Toons ... 🫶 Discord Server

ℹ️ This model's core idea was developed by Pipa by combining Galena Blend, JK, Helltaker, and QTori.

ℹ️ Recipe:

  1. Galena Blend v1.2.

  2. Added Loras: JK 0.25, Helltaker 0.25, QTori 1.2, with SuperMerger.

  3. Added BeautyRaccoonMix v1 0.25.

  4. Added Mistoon_Anime 0.20.

  5. Add Difference 0.2, with Loras from step 2, minus Galena Blend from step 1.

  6. Added Babes Kissable Lips 0.15.

  7. Baked VAE kl-f8-anime2.

📌 Are your results not 100% identical to any specific picture?

  1. Make sure to use Hires-fix from example SwinIR_4x / 4x-UltraSharp / 4x-AnimeSharp / RealESRGAN_x4plus_anime_6B (Upscaler Download), it is what I usually use for hires-fix.

  2. VAE is included inside. Use VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned for better colors. Download it into "stable-diffusion-webui/models/VAE" folder. Select it in the settings.

  3. I use xformers - it's a small performance improvement that might change the results. It is not a must to have and can be hard to install. Can be enabled with a command argument "--xformers" when launching WebUI.

  4. WebUI is updated constantly with some changes that influence image generation. Many times technological progress is prioritized over backward compatibility.

  5. Hardware differences may influence changes. I've heard that a bunch of people tested the same prompt with the same settings, and the results weren't identical.

  6. I have seen on my own system, that when running as part of a batch, may change a little bit the results.

  7. I suspect there are hidden variables inside modules we can't change that produce slightly different results due to internal state changes.

  8. Any change in image dimension, steps, sampler, prompt, and many other things, can cause small or huge differences in results.

📌 Do you really want to get the exact result from the image? There are a few things that you can do, and possibly get even better results.

  1. Make a single word changes to prompt/negative prompt and test, and push it slowly to your desired direction.

  2. If the image has too much of something or doesn't have enough of something, try to use emphasis. For example, too glossy? use "(glossy:0.8)", or less, or remove it from the prompt, or add it to the negative. Want more, use values 1.1-1.4, then additional descriptors in the same direction.

  3. Use variations - use the same seed, and to the right of the seed check "Extra". Set "Variation strength" to a low value of 0.05, generate a few images, and watch how big the changes are. Increase if you want more changes, and reduce if you want fewer changes. That way you can generate a huge amount of images that are very similar to the original, but some of them will be even better.

📌 Recommendations to improve your results:

  1. VAE is included inside. Use VAE for better colors and details. You can use VAE that comes with the model or download "vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned from (https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/sd-vae-ft-mse-original/tree/main) , ckpt or safetensors file into "stable-diffusion-webui/models/VAE" folder. In the settings find "SD VAE", refresh it, and select "vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned"(or the version included with the model). Click "Apply settings" button on the top. The VAE that comes with the model is "vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned", you don't need both, use the one that you downloaded, it will work very well with most of the other models too.

  2. Use hires-fix, SwinIR_4x / 4x-UltraSharp / 4x-AnimeSharp / RealESRGAN_x4plus_anime_6B (Upscaler Download), first pass around 512x512, second above 960x960, and keep the ratio between the two passes the same if possible.

  3. Use negatives, but not too much. Add them when you see something you don't like.

  4. Use CFG 7.5 or lower, with heavy prompts, that use many emphases and are long, you can go as low as 3.5. And generally try to minimize the usage of emphasis, you can just put the more important things at the begging of the prompt. If everything is important, just don't use emphasis at all.

  5. Make changes cautiously, changes made at the beginning of the prompt have more influence. So every concept can throw your results drastically.

  6. Read and use the manual.

  7. Learn from others, copy prompts from images that look good, and play with them.

  8. DPM++ 2M Karras is the sampler of choice for many people, including me. 40 steps are plenty, and I usually use 20.

  9. Discord server for help, sharing, show-offs, experiments, and challenges.

重要提醒：建議之前所有使用這個LoRA地用戶下載新地V2.5版本，新地版本經過LoRA Block Weight調整，既保留臉部效果又减小了對服飾、背景、風格地侵染。

The name "Pure Innocent Girl" is given because it is not a specific character's face, but rather a blend of styles that can produce a young and beautiful innocent girl's face, and a more natural and realistic (less plastic surgery sensation) oval face; It is necessary to enable Face restoration, with a weight between 0.25 and 0.85. The higher the weight, the more likely it is to produce childish features that look too childish. It is recommended to use it alone with a value of 0.5, and the maximum value should not exceed 0.9. If abnormalities occur when using it with other models, Lora, or certain samplers, it is recommended to randomly adjust the weight.Otherwise, there will be deviations that affect the style. Suitable for semi realistic and realistic effects, but not tested in anime styles.

If you like this LoRA, please leave a comment or image!

取名叫“純真女孩”，是因為它不是特定人物的臉，而是更像一種風格混合，能產生年輕美麗的清純少女臉，並且是更自然真實（整形手術感覺更少）的鵝蛋臉；一定要開啟臉部修復，權重在0.25～0.85之間，越高越容易產生看起來太孩子氣的幼稚特徵，單獨使用建議0.5，最高不要超過0.9，否則會產生偏差影響風格。如果搭配其它模型、Lora或者某些採樣器使用發生了异常，建議隨機調整權重。適合半寫實和逼真效果，但並沒有在動漫風格中測試。

items.description:
Dressed animals refer to animals that have been adorned or outfitted with clothing or accessories for various purposes, including entertainment, cultural traditions, or artistic expression. This practice has a long history and can be found in different cultures around the world.

In some cases, dressing animals is done for practical reasons, such as protecting them from harsh weather conditions or providing them with specialized gear for specific tasks, such as working animals or therapy animals. For example, horses may be dressed in saddles and bridles for riding, or guide dogs may wear special harnesses.

However, there is also a long tradition of dressing animals for decorative or symbolic purposes. This can be seen in various cultural practices, such as costumes worn by performing animals in circuses or costumes used in traditional ceremonies and festivals involving animals.

Dressing animals can also be seen in artistic and creative contexts. Artists may create whimsical or fantastical scenes by dressing animals in elaborate costumes or outfits, blurring the boundaries between reality and imagination. This can be seen in various forms of visual art, such as paintings, illustrations, or sculptures.

While dressing animals can sometimes raise ethical considerations, particularly when it involves discomfort or harm to the animals, in many cases it is done with care and respect for the well-being of the animals involved. In artistic and creative contexts, dressing animals can serve as a form of expression, adding a touch of whimsy, humor, or beauty to the depiction of animals in art.

Overall, dressed animals reflect the diverse ways in which humans interact with and represent the animal kingdom, blending practicality, cultural significance, and artistic expression.

items.name: Surreal Collage
items.description:
Surreal collage is an artistic technique that involves combining disparate and unexpected elements to create imaginative and dreamlike compositions. It is a form of collage art where the artist assembles various images, textures, and materials to construct a visual narrative that transcends reality and explores the subconscious mind.

In surreal collage, artists often borrow images from different sources such as vintage photographs, magazines, illustrations, and found objects. They manipulate and juxtapose these elements in unconventional ways, often defying the laws of physics and creating surreal and dreamlike scenes. By combining unrelated objects and contexts, they create a sense of surprise, mystery, and sometimes even a touch of humor.

The purpose of surreal collage is to challenge the viewer's perception and invite them into a world of imagination and fantasy. The unexpected combinations and juxtapositions can evoke a sense of disorientation, prompting viewers to question reality and explore the depths of their own imagination. Symbolism, metaphor, and visual poetry are often integral to the narrative of surreal collage, inviting viewers to interpret the artwork in their own unique way.

Surreal collage has a rich history, with notable artists such as Max Ernst, Hannah Höch, and René Magritte contributing to its development. The technique continues to be embraced by contemporary artists who seek to explore the subconscious mind, challenge traditional notions of reality, and create thought-provoking and visually striking compositions.

Whether exploring themes of identity, dreams, social commentary, or personal experiences, surreal collage offers artists a boundless creative space to express their inner visions and transport viewers to extraordinary realms. It celebrates the power of imagination, the unexpected connections between seemingly unrelated elements, and the limitless possibilities of artistic expression.
